## Math Formatting

**Always use LaTeX for mathematical expressions** — in all output, including
conversation responses and file content. Use `$...$` for inline math and
`$$...$$` for display math. Never write math as plain text (e.g. write
`$E[Y(1) - Y(0)]$` not `E[Y(1) - Y(0)]`).

